    This guide covers everything you do once Heather hands a vehicle off to you — checking eligibility, filing titles with the BMV, setting vehicle disposition (sell, junk, or hold), and routing vehicles through the auction pipeline. Follow it top to bottom on your first day.
  </div>
</div>

